panels.description: The average amount of heap allocated memory  for each engine.
panels.title: Memory Usage

panels.description: The average number of objects in memory for each engine.
panels.title: Objects

panels.description: Average number of objects created per second by each engine within the interval.  Only TEs create new objects.
panels.title: Created

panels.description: Average number of objects dropped per second by each engine within the interval.   Objects are dropped by garbage collector to make room for new objects to be created or imported.
panels.title: Dropped

panels.description: Above the x-axis is the average number of objects per second loaded into each SM.  Below the x-axis list the number of objects reloaded into each SM.  An object is reloaded if it was purged from SM memory and a TE already has that object in memory.
panels.title: Loaded / Reloaded

panels.description: Average number of objects purged from each SM.  An object is purged if the garbage collector needs to free up space and an object is removed from cache but still exist in cache within a TE. Below the x-axis is a count of the number of objects dropped that were in the purged state for each SM.

targets.query: SELECT mean("rate") FROM "ObjectsPurged" WHERE ("nodetype" = 'Storage' AND "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "db" =~ /^$database$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "host", "db", "nodeid", "startid" fill(null)

SELECT mean("rate") FROM "ObjectsDroppedPurged" WHERE ("nodetype" = 'Storage' AND "host" =~ /^$host$/ AND "db" =~ /^$database$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "host", "db", "nodeid", "startid" fill(null)

panels.title: Purged / Dropped Purged

panels.description: Average number of objects per second imported into an engine.   Objects are imported into a TE when a TE needs an existing object that is not in its local cache.  Objects are imported into an SM when a TE creates new objects.
panels.title: Imported

panels.description: Average number of objects per second exported into an engine.   Objects are exported from a TE or SM when another engine needs an object that is not in its local cache.  A TE will export newly created objects to all SMs.
panels.title: Exported

list.label: Database
list.name: database
list.query: select distinct("db") from (select first(raw) from "Milliseconds" where $timeFilter GROUP BY "db")

list.label: Host
list.name: host
list.query: select distinct("host") from (select first(raw) from "Milliseconds" where $timeFilter AND db =~ /$database$/ GROUP BY "host")
